2	// Covers: SleepDateKey boundaries, baseline correctness, best-version gating,
3	// rollup exclusion of unknown/skipped, insights caveat, migration idempotency,
4	// and locale round-trip safety.
5	//
6	// Environment requirement: tests are pure in-memory (no SwiftData, no HK).
7	// Run via: xcodebuild -scheme Better test -only-testing:BetterTests/ProtocolFormulaTrackingTests
